summary: This ENB are builded for Mid/High-End computer
descriptionHtml:
[center]
This ENB will offer you to enjoy Skyrim with good performance while maintaining a realistic and simple graphic quality.This ENB is optimized for new generation computers you can operate this ENB with a medium-range graphics card (GTX 760) without too much loss of performance[/center]

[size=4][center]--------------------------------[/center][/size]How to instal this:
1: open rar files and copy all files of "Skyrim" folder to C:\SteamLibrary\steamapps\common\Skyrim 
2: set bFloatPointRenderTarget=1 of SkyrimPrefs.ini
